Package: daos
Title: Utility Functions for Statistical Work
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Madsen", email = "danielmadsen@live.dk",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of utility functions for day-to-day statistical work.
    Includes helpers for file I/O across many formats, data validation
    checkpoints, duplicate detection, CPR number parsing, interactive
    time-series screening, and various convenience shortcuts for common
    tidyverse patterns.
